[01:43.180]feeding its flown young as it flies, | 一边飞行一边喂养飞翔的雏鸟，
[01:45.920]and slipping through a medium that seems to help its passage even when the wind is adverse. | 在似乎有助于其前进的介质中穿梭，即使风向不利。
[01:52.330]Such birds do us good. | 这样的鸟对我们有益。
